      <p class="bold">WEEK 7: Connect and Build</p>
      <h1>My to-do lists for the week as followed:</h1>
      <p>— Build the soft materials</p>
      <p>— Build the hardwares</p>
      <p>— Connect the hardwares and softwares</p>
      <p>— Set up with the projector</p>
      <p>— Debug and finalize the code</p>
      <h1>For the soft materials:</h1>
      <p>I find stitching often takes geometric shapes. I decided to embroider the pressing buttons, using traditional methods learned from the inspirational book by... The buttons were embroidered in the shapes resembling the patterns projected on the fabric.</p>
      <h1>For the hardware:</h1>
      <p>Build an electronic board that connects with Arduino.</p>
      <h1>For the code:</h1>
      <p>Map values from Aruino to Processing</p>
